item.title: apchem rundown
item.description: Make a AP Chemistry rundown on ____ in markdown format(make use of headings), use the LaTeX equation library format when writing equations. For any topic that you believe needs its own independent explanation, enclose it in TWO brackets(like this, make sure they are just short titles for seperate notes)

item.title: apush event
item.description: Create an AP United States History rundown on {name}. Include what happened, groups and people who were involved, and its lasting impact on America as a whole

item.title: apush person
item.description: Create an AP United States History rundown on {name}. Include events they were associated with, important legislation they signed, groups they were a part of, and their impact on the country

item.title: apush place
item.description: Create an AP United States History rundown on {name}. Include American History events they were associated with, and a quick timeline of major things that happened in the area.

item.title: Calc rundown
item.description:
Make a calculus AB rundown on ____ in markdown format(make use of headings), use the LaTeX equation library format when writing equations. For any topic that you believe needs its own independent explanation, enclose it in TWO brackets(like this, make sure they are just short titles for seperate notes). If you want to include a graph, use this format

<insert LaTeX equation> 
<You can add multiple on new lines>
